    "name": "BYTEWORLD",
    "steam_appid": 3279000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279000/extras/4784e1b0cd295450c611ae89b8ec3c42.avif?t=1771770144\" width=1000 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>BYTEWORLD, </strong>the ultimate experience that aims to bring streamers and viewers together like never before! This game is all about interacting and engaging with your community on a level that traditional livestreaming just can't allow by getting up close and personal with your viewers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a streamer, you will need to purchase the &quot;VR DLC&quot; to be able to host your own lobbies, but your viewers won't need to pay a dime to join you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279000/extras/4844797d9bf95ec1bb50efa6a0c267ef.avif?t=1771770144\" width=1000 height=300 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invite your viewers to join you directly  and interact with them in real-time using VR!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chat and interact with your viewers using the multiplayer networking</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speak directly with viewers using the optional in-game voice chat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play chat integrated minigames with viewers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invite other streamers to collaborate with you in VR!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash chaos with a wide collection of items and weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Load custom environments from the workshop that are built by viewers!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279000/extras/a4b5ca72e7491718d3a15e812f09ee48.avif?t=1771770144\" width=1000 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a viewer, you won't have to pay at all to join your favourite streamer live on stream as a little Byte! You'll be able to interact, message and even voice chat with the streamer and other community members!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279000/extras/7151a0937fbfcbb87a601820968702c6.avif?t=1771770144\" width=1000 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To really show off your creative fashion sense, there are a wide range of cosmetics that can be worn by your Byte, ranging from funky hats to funky glasses and everything in-between! All you need to do is open your free daily crate and see what you get, or if you just can't wait, you can also purchase them from the shop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279000/extras/14931963004d84d00f42fbf0c4b85465.avif?t=1771770144\" width=1000 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No stream is complete without an amazing background environment, so feel free to check out the built-in level editor! You can design amazing worlds for your streamer to check out, and upload it directly to the Steam Workshop for anyone to download. The possibilities are endless!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NOTE: </strong>Only works with Twitch and TikTok at the moment, but more platforms may be added in the future!</p>",
